  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this project is to study, in patients with rheumatoid arthritis, the
      effects of an intermittent type exercise associated with cryotherapy on the level of
      inflammation during its recovery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
